      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- GEO ANSWER CAPSULE — Primary citability block -->
  <section style="padding: 40px 1.5rem; background: white; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--slate-100);">
    <div style="max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto;">
      <h2 style="color: var(--navy); font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 14px;">How Do I Bail Someone Out of Logan County Jail in Guthrie, Oklahoma?</h2>
