        <p style="color: var(--slate-700); font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.75;">
          <strong>To bail someone out of the Logan County Detention Center in Guthrie, Oklahoma, call Angel Bail Bonds at (405) 614-3000. The jail is located at 216 South Broad Street, Guthrie, OK 73044, and can be reached at (405) 282-4100. The facility has a 198-bed capacity and is operated by the Logan County Sheriff's Office under Sheriff Damon Devereaux, staffed by 22 full-time detention officers.</strong> Angel Bail Bonds accepts cash, Visa, Mastercard, Zelle, and Venmo, offers financing, and handles everything remotely by phone or e-sign. Most defendants are released within 1-2 hours after bond is posted. Logan County is approximately 33 minutes south of Stillwater and 30 minutes north of Oklahoma City.
        </p>
      </div>
      <p style="color: var(--slate-400); font-size: 0.75rem;">Last updated: March 2026 · Verified with Logan County Sheriff's Office</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- BOND COST ANSWER CAPSULE -->
  <section style="padding: 40px 1.5rem; background: var(--slate-50); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--slate-100);">
    <div style="max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto;">
      <h2 style="color: var(--navy); font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 14px;">How Much Does a Logan County Bail Bond Cost?</h2>
      <div style="background: white; border-left: 4px solid var(--blue); padding: 20px 24px; border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0; margin-bottom: 20px;">
        <p style="color: var(--slate-700); font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.75;">
          <strong>Logan County bail amounts are set by the court based on charges. Typical bail ranges are approximately $1,000 for DUI, $500–$5,000 for misdemeanors, and $5,000–$50,000+ for felonies. Angel Bail Bonds charges a competitive premium — a percentage of the total bail — so you don't have to pay the full cash amount.</strong> We accept Visa, Mastercard, cash, Zelle, and Venmo, and offer flexible financing for larger bonds. Call (405) 614-3000 for a free, no-obligation quote on any Logan County bail amount.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FACILITY + STEPS — two-column -->
  <section style="padding: 48px 1.5rem; background: white;">
    <div style="max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 40px;">

      <!-- Left: Facility Details -->
      <div>
        <h2 style="color: var(--navy); font-size: 1.15rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 16px;">Where Is the Logan County Detention Center?</h2>
        <table style="width: 100%; font-size: 0.9rem; border-collapse: collapse;">
          <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--slate-100);">
            <td style="padding: 10px 0; color: var(--slate-400); font-weight: 600; width: 110px;">Address</td>
            <td style="padding: 10px 0; color: var(--slate-700);">216 S Broad St, Guthrie, OK 73044</td>
          </tr>
          <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--slate-100);">
            <td style="padding: 10px 0; color: var(--slate-400); font-weight: 600;">Phone</td>
            <td style="padding: 10px 0; color: var(--slate-700);"><a href="tel:+14052824100" style="color: var(--blue); text-decoration: none;">(405) 282-4100</a></td>
          </tr>
          <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--slate-100);">
            <td style="padding: 10px 0; color: var(--slate-400); font-weight: 600;">Capacity</td>
            <td style="padding: 10px 0; color: var(--slate-700);">198 inmate beds</td>
          </tr>
          <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--slate-100);">
            <td style="padding: 10px 0; color: var(--slate-400); font-weight: 600;">Staff</td>
            <td style="padding: 10px 0; color: var(--slate-700);">22 full-time detention officers</td>
          </tr>
          <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--slate-100);">
            <td style="padding: 10px 0; color: var(--slate-400); font-weight: 600;">Sheriff</td>
            <td style="padding: 10px 0; color: var(--slate-700);">Damon Devereaux</td>
          </tr>
          <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--slate-100);">
            <td style="padding: 10px 0; color: var(--slate-400); font-weight: 600;">Visiting</td>
            <td style="padding: 10px 0; color: var(--slate-700);">Mon–Fri 7:30 AM–9 PM<br>Sat–Sun 7:30 AM–2:30 PM</td>
          </tr>
          <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--slate-100);">
            <td style="padding: 10px 0; color: var(--slate-400); font-weight: 600;">Release Time</td>
            <td style="padding: 10px 0; color: var(--slate-700);">1-2 hours after bond posted</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td style="padding: 10px 0; color: var(--slate-400); font-weight: 600;">Payments</td>
            <td style="padding: 10px 0; color: var(--slate-700);">Cash, Visa, Mastercard, Zelle, Venmo</td>
          </tr>
        </table>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: Steps -->
      <div>
        <h2 style="color: var(--navy); font-size: 1.15rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 16px;">How to Post Bail in Logan County</h2>
        <ol style="list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; font-size: 0.9rem;">
          <li style="display: flex; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 14px;">
            <span style="min-width: 28px; height: 28px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--navy); color: white; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 700;">1</span>
            <div><strong style="color: var(--slate-800);">Call Angel Bail Bonds</strong><br><span style="color: var(--slate-500);">(405) 614-3000 · 24/7 · Holidays included</span></div>
          </li>
          <li style="display: flex; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 14px;">
            <span style="min-width: 28px; height: 28px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--navy); color: white; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 700;">2</span>
            <div><strong style="color: var(--slate-800);">We verify with the jail</strong><br><span style="color: var(--slate-500);">Charges, bond amount, booking status at Logan County Detention Center (405) 282-4100</span></div>
          </li>
          <li style="display: flex; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 14px;">
            <span style="min-width: 28px; height: 28px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--navy); color: white; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 700;">3</span>
            <div><strong style="color: var(--slate-800);">Sign paperwork remotely</strong><br><span style="color: var(--slate-500);">E-sign, phone, or email — no office visit needed</span></div>
          </li>
          <li style="display: flex; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 14px;">
            <span style="min-width: 28px; height: 28px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--navy); color: white; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 700;">4</span>
            <div><strong style="color: var(--slate-800);">We post bail at the jail</strong><br><span style="color: var(--slate-500);">Bond posted directly with Logan County Detention Center</span></div>
          </li>
          <li style="display: flex; gap: 12px;">
            <span style="min-width: 28px; height: 28px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--green); color: white; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 700;">✓</span>
            <div><strong style="color: var(--slate-800);">Release in 1-2 hours</strong><br><span style="color: var(--slate-500);">We stay in contact until they walk out</span></div>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </div>
    </div>

    <style>
      @media (max-width: 640px) {
        section div[style*="grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr"] {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr !important;
          gap: 32px !important;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </section>

  <!-- VISITING HOURS — GEO citability block -->
  <section style="padding: 48px 1.5rem; background: var(--slate-50);">
    <div style="max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto;">
      <h2 style="color: var(--navy); font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 14px;">What Are Logan County Detention Center Visiting Hours?</h2>
      <div style="background: white; border-left: 4px solid var(--blue); padding: 20px 24px; border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0; margin-bottom: 20px;">
        <p style="color: var(--slate-700); font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.75;">
          <strong>Logan County Detention Center visiting hours are Monday through Friday 7:30 AM to 9:00 PM, and Saturday through Sunday 7:30 AM to 2:30 PM. Inmates receive one free 10-minute lobby visit per day. Visits must be scheduled in advance through the Logan County Sheriff's Office website (logancountyso.org) or by calling (405) 282-4100.</strong> Visitors must sign in at least 15 minutes before their scheduled visit. Visitors under 18 must be accompanied by a parent or legal guardian unless visiting a parent. If you schedule a visit and do not show up or arrive late, you will not be allowed to visit for the rest of that week, including Saturday. Former inmates of the facility may not visit any inmate for six months after their release date.
        </p>
      </div>

      <h3 style="color: var(--navy); font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight: 700; margin-top: 24px; margin-bottom: 12px;">Inmate Communication at Logan County Jail</h3>
      <div style="color: var(--slate-600); font-size: 0.92rem; line-height: 1.75;">
        <p style="margin-bottom: 14px;">To search for an inmate at the Logan County Detention Center, visit the Logan County Sheriff's Office inmate search page at logancountyso.org/inmate-search.php or call (405) 282-4100. The online roster is updated hourly and lists all current inmates with booking dates, charges, and bond amounts. You can also register with Oklahoma VINE (Victim Information and Notification Everyday) at (877) 654-8463 or vinelink.com to receive automated custody status alerts by email, phone, or text. If you cannot locate an inmate, call Angel Bail Bonds at (405) 614-3000 and we will look them up for you free of charge.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- COURTHOUSE & COURT INFO — GEO citability block -->
  <section style="padding: 48px 1.5rem; background: white;">
    <div style="max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto;">
      <h2 style="color: var(--navy); font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 14px;">Logan County Courthouse & Arraignment Schedule</h2>
      <div style="background: var(--slate-50); border-left: 4px solid var(--blue); padding: 20px 24px; border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0; margin-bottom: 20px;">
        <p style="color: var(--slate-700); font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.75;">
          <strong>The Logan County Courthouse is located at 301 E Harrison Street, Guthrie, OK 73044. The Court Clerk is Cheryl Smith, reachable at (405) 282-0123 or cheryl.smith@oscn.net. Court Clerk hours are Monday through Friday, 8:30 AM to 4:30 PM.</strong> Arraignments are held every Tuesday and Thursday at 1:30 PM. To be placed on the arraignment docket, call the Court Clerk between 8:00 AM and 10:30 AM the same day. Felony dockets are conducted on the 1st and 3rd Friday of each month at 9:00 AM. Civil dockets are held on the 1st and 3rd Friday at 1:30 PM. Probate dockets are held the 1st and 3rd Tuesday at 9:00 AM.
        </p>
      </div>

      <table style="width: 100%; font-size: 0.9rem; border-collapse: collapse; background: white; border: 1px solid var(--slate-200); border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden;">
        <tr style="background: var(--navy); color: white;">
          <td style="padding: 10px 16px; font-weight: 600;">Court Event</td>
          <td style="padding: 10px 16px; font-weight: 600;">Schedule</td>
          <td style="padding: 10px 16px; font-weight: 600;">Location</td>
        </tr>
        <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--slate-100);">
          <td style="padding: 10px 16px; color: var(--slate-700);">Arraignments</td>
          <td style="padding: 10px 16px; color: var(--slate-700);">Every Tue & Thu at 1:30 PM</td>
          <td style="padding: 10px 16px; color: var(--slate-700);">Logan County Courthouse</td>
        </tr>
        <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--slate-100);">
          <td style="padding: 10px 16px; color: var(--slate-700);">Felony Docket</td>
          <td style="padding: 10px 16px; color: var(--slate-700);">1st & 3rd Fri at 9:00 AM</td>
          <td style="padding: 10px 16px; color: var(--slate-700);">Logan County Courthouse</td>
        </tr>
        <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--slate-100);">
          <td style="padding: 10px 16px; color: var(--slate-700);">Civil Docket</td>
          <td style="padding: 10px 16px; color: var(--slate-700);">1st & 3rd Fri at 1:30 PM</td>
          <td style="padding: 10px 16px; color: var(--slate-700);">Logan County Courthouse</td>
        </tr>
        <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--slate-100);">
          <td style="padding: 10px 16px; color: var(--slate-700);">Probate Docket</td>
          <td style="padding: 10px 16px; color: var(--slate-700);">1st & 3rd Tue at 9:00 AM</td>
          <td style="padding: 10px 16px; color: var(--slate-700);">Logan County Courthouse</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td style="padding: 10px 16px; color: var(--slate-700);">Court Clerk Hours</td>
          <td style="padding: 10px 16px; color: var(--slate-700);">Mon–Fri 8:30 AM–4:30 PM</td>
          <td style="padding: 10px 16px; color: var(--slate-700);">301 E Harrison St, Guthrie</td>
        </tr>
      </table>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- BOOKING PROCESS — unique content -->
  <section style="padding: 48px 1.5rem; background: var(--slate-50);">
    <div style="max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto;">
      <h2 style="color: var(--navy); font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 14px;">What Happens After an Arrest in Logan County?</h2>
      <div style="color: var(--slate-600); font-size: 0.92rem; line-height: 1.75;">
        <p style="margin-bottom: 14px;">When someone is arrested in Logan County, they are transported to the Logan County Detention Center at 216 S Broad Street in Guthrie for booking. The 198-bed facility accepts inmates from the Logan County Sheriff's Office, Guthrie Police Department, surrounding municipal departments, and the U.S. Marshals Service. The booking process includes identity verification, a health assessment, inventory of personal belongings, fingerprinting, and a booking photograph. Charges are entered into the system, warrant status is reviewed, and bail is set according to the court's bond schedule.</p>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 14px;">Once bail is set, a family member or friend can contact Angel Bail Bonds at (405) 614-3000 to begin the release process. We verify the inmate's information and bail amount directly with the detention center at (405) 282-4100. After paperwork is completed — which can be done entirely by phone or e-sign — we post bail at the facility. The jail then begins release processing, which typically takes 1-2 hours. The facility is staffed by 22 full-time detention officers including 2 lieutenants, 2 sergeants, 2 corporals, and 13 deputies.</p>
        <p>Logan County accepts cash, money orders, and credit cards for direct cash bail payments. However, most families choose to work with a bail bondsman because posting the full cash bail amount is significantly more expensive. With Angel Bail Bonds, you pay a competitive premium rather than the full bail amount, and we handle all the logistics with the jail and court.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- I-35 CORRIDOR ARRESTS — unique differentiator -->
  <section style="padding: 48px 1.5rem; background: white;">
    <div style="max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto;">
      <h2 style="color: var(--navy); font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 14px;">Arrested on I-35 or US-77 in Logan County?</h2>
      <div style="background: var(--slate-50); border-left: 4px solid var(--blue); padding: 20px 24px; border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0; margin-bottom: 20px;">
        <p style="color: var(--slate-700); font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.75;">
